<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>账户激活邮件</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .header p {
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .welcome-message {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .welcome-message h2 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .welcome-message p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .user-info {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        }
        
        .user-info h3 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .user-info p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            color: #555;
        }
        
        .activation-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .activation-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4CAF50, #45a049);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .activation-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .link-section {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .link-section h4 {
            color: #856404;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .link-section p {
            color: #856404;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .link-text {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 10px;
            word-break: break-all;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #495057;
        }
        
        .security-notice {
            background: #d1ecf1;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .security-notice h4 {
            color: #0c5460;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .security-notice ul {
            color: #0c5460;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        
        .security-notice li {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .footer .company-info {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 5px;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .activation-button {
                display: block;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🎉 欢迎！</h1>
            <p>很感谢您的支持，作为验证账户有效性的最后一步，还请您确认您的账户邮箱咩~</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="welcome-message">
                <h2>账户激活邮件</h2>
                <p>邮箱是找回密码，重置账户的关键信息，请您确认账户与邮箱匹配！</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="user-info">
                <h3>📋 在确认邮箱时，请您先确认以下信息</h3>
                <p><strong>用户名：</strong> {{ username }}</p>
                <p><strong>注册时间：</strong> {{ registration_time|default("刚刚") }}</p>
                <p><strong>账户状态：</strong> 待激活</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="activation-section">
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; color: #666;">
                    若信息无误即可点击按钮激活账户：
                </p>
                <a href="{{ activate_link }}" class="activation-button">
                    ✅ 激活账户
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="link-section">
                <h4>🔗 激活链接</h4>
                <p>如果按钮无法点击，请复制以下链接到浏览器地址栏后手动访问：</p>
                <div class="link-text">{{ activate_link }}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-notice">
                <h4>🔒 安全提示</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>此激活链接仅对您的账户有效，仅针对账户激活确认这一场景使用</li>
                    <li>激活链接仅可使用一次，请避免激活链接泄露</li>
                    <li>激活链接有效期为5分钟，超时请重新申请激活</li>
                    <li>如果您没有注册过账户，请忽略此邮件</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p class="company-info">{{ company_name|default("我们的平台") }}</p>
            <p>此邮件由系统自动发送，请勿直接回复</p>
            <p>如需帮助，请联系：{{ support_email|default("support@example.com") }}</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
                © {{ current_year|default("2025") }} {{ company_name|default("我们的平台") }}. 保留所有权利.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
